last_episode_to_air.name: Flesh and Blood
last_episode_to_air.overview: Nora takes the powerful Upload companies to court, but she may have bitten off more than she can chew.

name: Upload
overview: In 2033, people who are near death can be “uploaded” into virtual reality hotels run by 6 tech firms. Cash-strapped Nora lives in Brooklyn and works customer service for the luxurious “Lakeview” digital afterlife. When L.A. party-boy/coder Nathan’s self-driving car crashes, his high-maintenance girlfriend uploads him permanently into Nora’s VR world.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: Nathan is at a crossroads in his (after) life… his ex-girlfriend Ingrid has unexpectedly arrived to Lakeview hoping to strengthen their relationship, but his heart still secretly yearns for his customer service angel Nora. Meanwhile Nora is off the grid and involved with the anti-tech rebel group “The Ludds.”

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: Nora and a freshly downloaded Nathan navigate their relationship while racing to stop the mysterious conspiracy that threatens to destroy millions of lives.

episodes.name: Welcome to Upload
episodes.overview: After a self-driving car crash, Nathan is uploaded to Lakeview, his girlfriend’s family’s digital after-life, where he meets his customer service rep, Nora.

episodes.name: Five Stars
episodes.overview: Nora tries to get her ratings up, so her boss will approve her dad’s upload loan. Nathan acclimates to his new world with the help of a Lakeview therapist.

episodes.name: The Funeral
episodes.overview: Scientists attempt to download a consciousness back into a clone body. Nathan attends his own funeral and Nora uncovers a mystery surrounding his death.

episodes.name: The Sex Suit
episodes.overview: Nora thinks she may have misjudged Nathan. Nathan and his girlfriend Ingrid are interviewed about the challenges of romance between a living person and an Upload.

episodes.name: The Grey Market
episodes.overview: Nora’s Dad’s vape lung worsens while Nathan, his friend Luke, and Dylan, an uploaded teen whose body is not keeping up with his age, visit a hacker’s market in cyberspace.

episodes.name: The Sleepover
episodes.overview: Nathan is thrown when Nora goes on a Nitely date. Ingrid invites Nathan’s niece for a sleepover. Nathan and Nora suspect his damaged memories may lead to a greater conspiracy. Luke gets into a fight with Aleesha.

episodes.name: Bring Your Dad to Work Day
episodes.overview: Nathan takes Nora’s dad on a do-or-die upload decision tour, but things go awry when Luddites sabotage Lakeview. Nora does some sleuthing on Lucy’s computer in the confusion.

episodes.name: Shopping Other Digital After-Lives
episodes.overview: After a surprising revelation, Nathan shops for a new digital after-life. Nora travels to LA to help Ingrid stop him from leaving Lakeview.

episodes.name: Update Eve
episodes.overview: The Uploads are looking forward to the improvements in the new Lakeview Operating System. Nathan and Nora stay up late to recover Nathan’s missing memories.

episodes.name: Freeyond
episodes.overview: Nathan’s restored memories and shifting emotional allegiances put Nora in physical danger.

episodes.name: Welcome Back, Mr. Brown
episodes.overview: While living with Ingrid, Nathan searches for Nora, who has fled of the grid.

episodes.name: Dinner Party
episodes.overview: At a status-obsessed dinner, Nathan faces ghosts from his past. Nora flexes her programming skills as she steps into activism.

episodes.name: Robin Hood
episodes.overview: Frustrated with the inequities at Lakeview, Nathan and Luke decide to redistribute some wealth with Ingrid's unwitting help. Nora undertakes a secretive mission.

episodes.name: Family Day
episodes.overview: Nora's loyalties are stressed as she is called upon to take revolutionary action. Nathan's visiting family prompts him to consider what he wants out of his afterlife. Luke invents a new sport.

episodes.name: Mind Frisk
episodes.overview: Nathan and Nora race to stop a potentially dangerous technological advance. Luke boycotts sleep when he finds Horizen is profiting from his dreams, as Aleesha continues to rise in the Horizen hierarchy. Ingrid is tempted by a new tech offering: digital babies.

episodes.name: The Outing
episodes.overview: Nora and Aleesha pursue the mystery into New York City with Nathan and Luke along on screens. Ingrid receives unexpected visitors.

episodes.name: Download
episodes.overview: Nora rallies the support of unlikely allies and Hyperloops to LA. Meanwhile, the issues in Nathan's personal life come to a head.

2.name: Season 2
2.overview: Nathan is at a crossroads in his (after) life… his ex-girlfriend Ingrid has unexpectedly arrived to Lakeview hoping to strengthen their relationship, but his heart still secretly yearns for his customer service angel Nora. Meanwhile Nora is off the grid and involved with the anti-tech rebel group “The Ludds.”

episodes.name: Ticking Clock
episodes.overview: Nora and a recently downloaded Nathan race to stop Freeyond before his head explodes.

episodes.name: Strawberry
episodes.overview: Nathan and Nora struggle to make their relationship work, while Ingrid tries to make the best of her second shot at love.

episodes.name: CyberDiscountDay
episodes.overview: The gang celebrates CyberDiscountDay while Nora discovers something game-changing: Nathan has been copied in Lakeview.

episodes.name: Download Doctor
episodes.overview: Nathan and Nora track down the doctor who invented download, while Aleesha rises higher in the Horizen hierarchy. Ingrid and back-up Nathan grow closer.

episodes.name: Rescue Mission
episodes.overview: Nathan teams up with his own copy to save Luke, but Nora is discovered by the conspiracy.

episodes.name: Memory Crackers
episodes.overview: Nora and Nathan find important clues to expose Freeyond, but the search poses a challenge to their relationship.

episodes.name: Upload Day
episodes.overview: Nathan and Nora try to have a special last day together.

episodes.name: Flesh and Blood
episodes.overview: Nora takes the powerful Upload companies to court, but she may have bitten off more than she can chew.

3.overview: Nora and a freshly downloaded Nathan navigate their relationship while racing to stop the mysterious conspiracy that threatens to destroy millions of lives.
